import heapq

def mincostToHireWorkers(quality, wage, K):
    workers = sorted(([float(w) / q, q] for (w, q) in zip(wage, quality)))
    res = float('inf')
    qsum = 1
    queue = []
    for (r, q) in workers:
        heapq.heappush(queue, -q)
        qsum += q
        if len(queue) > K:
            qsum += heapq.heappop(queue)
        if len(queue) == K:
            res = min(res, qsum * r)
    return res
